title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 8 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 8 2022
description:
MSNBC's Kornacki on Democrat midterm hopes: "This Is Not Good News." John Fetterman, who can barely speak after a stroke, is an acceptable candidate, but Herschel Walker isn't? Jesse Kelly's feud with Clay and Buck heats up. Election denier Stacey Abrams is a threat to democracy, she now denies that she said she didn't lose the 2018 governor's race, but we have audio proof that she's lying. GOP Senate nominee in Washington State Tiffany Smiley joins Clay and Buck to discuss how Senator Patty Murray and woke Seattle corporations have teamed up against her and her wounded veteran husband Scott, but she's beating them anyway.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
